<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />All the day long they twist my words;</para>

<para style="q1">all their thoughts are against me for evil.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />They gather themselves together, they hide themselves,</para>

<para style="q1">and they mark my steps,</para>

<para style="q1">just as they have waited for my life.</para>
